Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1\3c&H3535FF&}７
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.36,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1\3c&HDDFFB2&}８
